# Summary
This documentation explains three methods for creating cohorts in Amplitude: using Microscope to create cohorts from chart data points, importing cohorts from CSV files (with specific formatting requirements), and creating inline behavioral/interval cohorts directly within the Segmentation module of most chart types.

